SELECT CASE object_info ->> '$.moduleName' WHEN 'lotNumber' THEN (select object_info->>'$.certificateLabel' as `lotNumber` from warehouse_lot_number where id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select object_info->>'$.certificateLabel' as `lotNumber` from warehouse_transfer_receipt where id = [work_order_id]) END AS lotNumber from warehouse_stock_transfer where id = [stock_id]

select 'lotNumber' as `module_name`, wln.id as `id`, wln.object_info->>'$.certificateLabel' as `lotNumber`, wln.object_info->>'$.lotId' as `lotId`, wln.object_info->>'$.internelLotNo' as `internelLotNo`, wits.object_info->>'$.name' as `testStatus`, wln.object_info->>'$.expiryDate' as `expiryDate`, im.object_info->>'$.stockInHand' as `stockInHand`, im.object_info->>'$.inventoryId' as `matId`, im.object_info->>'$.name' as `matName`, il.object_info->>'$.name' as `location`, uom.object_info->>'$.name' as `uom`  from warehouse_lot_number as wln left join warehouse_iot_test_status as wits on wln.object_info ->> '$.testStatus' = wits.id left join warehouse_material_receipt as imr on wln.object_info ->> '$.receiptId' = imr.id left join inventory_master as im on imr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_location as il on im.object_info ->> '$.location' = il.id left join inventory_uom as uom on im.object_info ->> '$.unitOfMeasure' = uom.id where wln.object_status = 'Active' union select 'transferReceipt' as `module_name`, wtr.id as `id`, wtr.object_info ->> '$.certificateLabel' as `lotNumber`, wtr.object_info ->> '$.lotId' as `lotId`, wtr.object_info ->> '$.internelLotNo' as `internelLotNo`,  wmrs.object_info ->> '$.name' as `testStatus`, wtr.object_info ->> '$.expiryDate' as `expiryDate`, im.object_info ->> '$.stockInHand' as `stockInHand`, im.object_info ->> '$.matId' as `matId`, im.object_info ->> '$.matName' as `matName`, il.object_info ->> '$.name' as `location`, uom.object_info ->> '$.name' as `uom` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr left join warehouse_material_receipt_status as wmrs on wtr.object_info ->> '$.status' = wmrs.id left join inventory_master as im on wtr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_location as il on im.object_info ->> '$.location' = il.id left join inventory_uom as uom on im.object_info ->> '$.unitOfMeasure' = uom.id where wtr.object_status = 'Active'

select il.id, il.object_info->>'$.locationId' as `locationId`,il.object_info->>'$.name' as `name`, il.object_info->>'$.locationCapacity' as `locationCapacity`, il.object_info->>'$.allowedCapacity' as `allowedCapacity`, isc.object_info->>'$.name' as `storageCondition` from inventory_location as il left join inventory_storage_condition as isc on il.object_info->>'$.storageCondition' = isc.id where il.object_status = 'Active'

SELECT result.material as `material` CASE WHEN '[module_name]' = 'lotNumber' THEN (select im.object_info->>'$.name' as `material` from warehouse_lot_number as wln left join inventory_material_receipt as imr on wln.object_info ->> '$.receipt' = imr.id left join inventory_master as im on imr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id where wln.id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select im.object_info->>'$.name' as `material` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr left join inventory_master as im on wtr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id  where wtr.id = [work_order_id]) END AS result

SELECT result.uom as `uom` CASE WHEN '[module_name]' = 'lotNumber' THEN (select uo.object_info->>'$.name' as `uom` from warehouse_lot_number as wln left join inventory_material_receipt as imr on wln.object_info ->> '$.receipt' = imr.id left join inventory_master as im on imr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_uom as uo on im.object_info ->> '$.unitOfMeasure' = uo.id where wln.id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select uo.object_info->>'$.name' as `uom` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr left join inventory_master as im on wtr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_uom as uo on im.object_info ->> '$.unitOfMeasure' = uo.id where wtr.id = [work_order_id]) END AS result

SELECT result.fromLoc as `fromLoc` CASE WHEN '[module_name]' = 'lotNumber' THEN (select il.object_info->>'$.name' as `fromLoc` from warehouse_lot_number as wln left join inventory_material_receipt as imr on wln.object_info ->> '$.receipt' = imr.id left join inventory_master as im on imr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_location as il on im.object_info ->> '$.location' = il.id where wln.id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select il.object_info->>'$.name' as `fromLoc` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr left join inventory_master as im on wtr.object_info ->> '$.material' = im.id left join inventory_location as il on im.object_info ->> '$.location' = il.id where wtr.id = [work_order_id]) END AS result

SELECT result.systemLotId as `systemLotId` CASE WHEN '[module_name]' = 'lotNumber' THEN (select uo.object_info->>'$.lotId' as `systemLotId` from warehouse_lot_number as wln where wln.id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select wtr.object_info->>'$.lotId' as `systemLotId` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr where wtr.id = [work_order_id]) END AS result

SELECT result.lotId as `lotId` CASE WHEN '[module_name]' = 'lotNumber' THEN (select uo.object_info->>'$.certificateLabel' as `lotId` from warehouse_lot_number as wln where wln.id = [work_order_id]) ELSE (select wtr.object_info->>'$.certificateLabel' as `lotId` from warehouse_transfer_receipt as wtr where wtr.id = [work_order_id]) END AS result
